{"tid":892141,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"食煙生肺癌係吹水，身邊食煙過廿年既好健康，但有兩個唔食煙既肺癌死","createTime":"2018-11-06T16:15:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-06T16:59:27.000Z","uid":134683,"like":2,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"73c3bd82469b1261af554dedcbf166520b8c2dea","tid":892141,"uid":134683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T16:15:06.000Z","msg":"仲要食左二十至四十年<br />\n面色、中氣樣樣好到不得了<br />\n唔睇d牙根本睇唔出係煙產<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n另外兩個冇食煙既就無咁好彩<br />\n一個30一個60幾歲死<br />\n發現已經係末期半年就走左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n到底係咪吹水架<br />\n又話吸煙致癌率高廿幾卅倍<br />\n點解我身邊既唔係咁既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd7ebb536c5c6ed2d015684e2c978239f9109b21","tid":892141,"uid":46042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T16:16:00.000Z","msg":"邱吉爾表示<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"954a1ac911641c1a4033806deb6e0a35696bd967","tid":892141,"uid":134683,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"dd7ebb536c5c6ed2d015684e2c978239f9109b21","tid":892141,"uid":46042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T16:16:00.000Z","msg":"邱吉爾表示<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T16:17:31.000Z","msg":"仲有鄧小平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b3b30893f96d31fa687a71f089b601d623f2396","tid":892141,"uid":177089,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T16:45:35.000Z","msg":"返工儲錢上車係吹水<br />\n身邊十幾個朋友返咗廿年工都買唔起樓<br />\n但識得個老闆日日唔返工都有幾層樓喺手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e76dcf859b21218a87afc1537970d99dc0aedfe","tid":892141,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5b3b30893f96d31fa687a71f089b601d623f2396","tid":892141,"uid":177089,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":